data.description: This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms, spans an impressive 2,166 square feet and was expertly built in 2020. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, one of the standout features of this residence is the added privacy with no rear neighbors, creating a peaceful oasis for you and your family. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the spacious and open floor plan offers a seamless flow between rooms, providing an inviting space for both entertaining and everyday living. The comfortable living room is the perfect spot to relax and unwind after a long day, while the adjacent dining area is ideal for hosting dinner parties with friends and family. Step outside to the beautiful backyard, with no rear neighbors, you can enjoy tranquil mornings and serene evenings on the patio, savoring the peacefulness of your own retreat. With its modern amenities, thoughtful design, and unmatched privacy, this house is the perfect opportunity for families seeking the pinnacle of contemporary living.
